WEBVTT

00:05.091 --> 00:09.292
We teamed up with a handful of the world's leading video scientists...

00:09.649 --> 00:11.520
...and created something really awesome.

00:12.695 --> 00:13.643
We call it "Cinema".

00:15.104 --> 00:17.565
Cinematic stabilization for your videos...

00:18.673 --> 00:20.702
...that will change video forever.

00:21.617 --> 00:22.750
Let me show you what I mean.

00:26.070 --> 00:28.005
This is us recording our video in the park.

00:29.329 --> 00:33.307
This is the normal video, and this is Cinema.

00:34.957 --> 00:37.230
Gorgeous, stabilized video for your iPhone.

00:37.323 --> 00:37.397
Go!

00:38.987 --> 00:40.032
This is the original.

00:40.930 --> 00:41.277
Faster.

00:41.505 --> 00:42.623
And this is with Instagram.

00:44.067 --> 00:45.593
It's completely mind-blowing.

00:47.168 --> 00:50.174
When you're running, chasing your kid, trying to get a beautiful video,...

00:51.170 --> 00:54.219
...now, you have the power of Cinema in your pocket.

00:55.780 --> 00:57.397
This changes everything.

00:59.135 --> 01:00.490
And I'm excited to bring you Cinema.

01:04.017 --> 01:08.269
Today, video on Instagram available for iOS and Android,...

01:09.239 --> 01:11.133
...15 seconds of beautiful video,...

01:11.348 --> 01:12.634
...13 custom filters.

01:13.264 --> 01:16.190
Select a cover frame to show the world what you recorded.

01:17.641 --> 01:19.833
And groundbreaking technology for video...

01:20.386 --> 01:23.619
...that changes video forever and makes your video beautiful.

01:24.269 --> 01:24.807
Cinema.

